dc_title_s: Detail map of the Upper Mississippi River from the mouth of the Ohio River to Minneapolis, Minnesota, v.2
dc_description_s: Survey of the Mississippi River; made under the direction of the Mississippi River Commission. Contains Charts 135-148, 150, 152-165, 167-168, 470-171, 177, 184-189. Each chart is at a scale of 1:20,000. Charts also show river depths and include an Authorities and Notes section. Some charts show land owners adjacent to the river.|63 x 101 centimeters|Scale 1:20,000.; Scale 1:10,000|General Map Collection
